General.Name: Lifestyle Communities Ltd
General.Description: Lifestyle Communities Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides housing for its homeowners in community in Australia. The company operates communities, including 21 in operation and 9 in planning or development. It serves working, semi-retired, and retired people. The company was formerly known as Namberry Limited and changed its name to Lifestyle Communities Limited in June 2007. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
